snippet.title: Broken Reality 2000 - Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Welcome back, user! It's been a while!

Broken Reality is back to take the new millenium by storm!
Surf the web, solve some puzzles, have some laughs and explore beautiful worlds in this state-of-the-art y2k simulator!

Check out our Steam Page: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2133850
And don't forget to join our Discord community: https://discord.gg/V6tAejg
